help
status 
  lock state, fabric count, last/trusted range

lock 
  drive the bolt to Locked

unlock 
  drive the bolt to Unlocked

codes 
  reprint the commissioning QR URL + manual pairing code

range 
  print the latest distance

aliro 
  aliro <prov|trust|clear>: show identity / trust last credential / empty trust
  store

uwbdiag 
  uwbdiag [on|off]: raw per-frame UWB trace (boot default off; costs slot
  deadlines)

log 
  log <tag|*> <level>: runtime log level (boot default warn)

factoryreset 
  erase all Matter state and reboot

clear 
  clear the screen (also: ctrl-L)

help  [<string>] [-v <0|1>]
  Print the summary of all registered commands if no arguments are given,
  otherwise print summary of given command.
      <string>  Name of command
  -v, --verbose=<0|1>  If specified, list console commands with given verbose level

